    INSTALLING TAR
    
    
    COMPRESSING DOCUMENTS FOR BACKUPS
$ tar -czf fileCompr.tgz *      #> Create and zip in file (-czf) fileCompr.tgz everything (*) 
$ zip -r School.zip School      #> Compress with zip file, but > than tar -czf 

$ gzip -l alpha_files.tgz       #> View the compressing detail
$ tar -tf folders.tgz           #> View the content of the file 

    DECOMPRESSING DOCUMENTS
$ tar -xzf fileCompr.tgz        #> Extract and unzip the file fileCompr.tgz
$ unzip -l School.zip           #> Unzip and list its content
